	<h1 class="title">西装到底要怎么穿，才能让你看起来不像卖保险的？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/399912/small/399912.JPG?1452046699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张田小 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-18 07:55:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15071/medium/15071.jpg?1442483017" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15071" data-title="《西装到底要怎么穿，才能让你看起来不像卖保险的？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15071/medium/15071.jpg?1442483017" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15071.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
